data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. A move-in-ready home in Seminole that offers not just a residence but a lifestyle, it boasts a prime location just minutes away from the pristine white sand beaches, premier shopping destinations, and the popular Tyrone Mall. As you step inside this charming abode, you'll be greeted by 1,399 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space. The tile flooring seamlessly connects the living room, kitchen, and dining area, creating a cohesive and stylish atmosphere throughout. The open-style kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, featuring a breakfast island, granite counters, solid wood cabinets, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Whether you're entertaining guests or preparing a family meal, this kitchen is sure to inspire culinary creativity. The home offers three spacious bedrooms, each thoughtfully designed for comfort. Two guest bedrooms feature beautiful laminate flooring, providing a warm and welcoming ambiance. The guest bathroom boasts a tub/shower combination, catering to both relaxation and convenience. The master bedroom offers a tranquil retreat with its laminate floors and an en-suite bathroom that has just been tastefully redone. This home comes with practical updates, including a 2-year-old flat roof, a 4-year-old AC system, and a nearly 2-year-old water heater. These features ensure peace of mind and efficiency for years to come. Step outside to the screened-in patio, perfect for enjoying the Florida sunshine and entertaining guests in a bug-free environment. The well for irrigation keeps the lush landscaping looking vibrant and green while minimizing water costs. The convenience of a one-car garage adds a practical touch to your everyday living. What's even more enticing is the absence of both HOA and CDD fees, allowing you to enjoy your property without any additional financial burden. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning Seminole residence your own. Schedule a showing today!
